{
  "texts": [
    "This, in turn, will make existing (S&A) units the bottleneck in the pipelined implementation.",
    "We also incorporate additional registers dedicated to storing the quantization constants to dequantize the value.",
    "Conventionally, the current through the crossbar bit lines is converted to digital values through an ADC.",
    "Subsequently, the output is obtained by performing bitwise S&A operations and stored in the output register.",
    "Our proposed modification introduces an extra computation cycle in this process."
  ]
}